Lanxess Posts Higher Fourth-Quarter Net, Raises Dividend

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-03-17T06:30:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/lanxess-posts-higher-fourth-quarter-net-raises-dividend.html
  Lanxess AG (LXS)  said fourth-quarter net
income rose to 26 million euros from 14 million euros. Revenue
increased, the company said in a statement handed to reporters
today.  The company proposed a 40 percent dividend increase, to 70
cents, and said it expects 2011 sales and earnings before
interest, taxes, depreciation and amortization and excluding
one-time items to increase.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story:
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf at 
